The '''triumvirate''' was a group of three [[Democratic Alliance]] officials who assumed power over the [[Five Worlds]] following the assassination of [[Dur Gejjen]]. The reason they assumed power was that, after the deaths of so many [[Five World Prime Minister]]s in such a short span of time, no one wished to assume the post. However, soon afterward [[Sadras Koyan]] was elected as Five Worlds Prime Minister, apparently replacing the Triumvirate.

